00:18:51,364 --> 00:18:53,499
where everything's
great all the time.

266
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:55,467
Zuko, leave her alone.

267
00:18:55,468 --> 00:18:57,136
I'm so pretty, look at me.

268
00:18:57,137 --> 00:18:58,971
I can walk on my hands, whoo!

269
00:19:02,142 --> 00:19:03,676
Circus freak.

270
00:19:05,779 --> 00:19:07,546
Yes, I'm a circus freak.

271
00:19:07,647 --> 00:19:09,848
Go ahead and laugh
all you want.

272
00:19:09,949 --> 00:19:11,939
You wanna know why
I joined the circus?

