I was scared of spending
the rest of my life

280
00:19:26,866 --> 00:19:28,801
as part of a matched set.

281
00:19:28,902 --> 00:19:30,436
At least, I'm different now.

282
00:19:30,537 --> 00:19:33,305
Circus freak is a compliment.

283
00:19:33,406 --> 00:19:36,775
Guess that explains why you
need 10 boyfriends, too.

284
00:19:36,876 --> 00:19:38,577
I'm sorry, what?

285
00:19:38,678 --> 00:19:40,346
Attention issues?

286
00:19:40,347 --> 00:19:42,381
You couldn't get enough
attention when you were a kid

287
00:19:42,382 --> 00:19:44,950
so you're trying
to make up for it now.

288
00:19:45,051 --> 00:19:47,986
Well, what's your excuse, mai?

289
00:19:48,088 --> 00:19:50,389
You were an only child
for 15 years.

290
00:19:50,390 --> 00:19:52,091
But even with all that attention

