335
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:36,929
I'm angrier than ever
and I don't know why.

336
00:21:36,930 --> 00:21:39,298
There's a simple question
you need to answer then.

337
00:21:39,299 --> 00:21:40,733
Who are you angry at?

338
00:21:40,834 --> 00:21:43,435
No one, I'm just angry.

339
00:21:43,536 --> 00:21:46,238
Yeah, who are you
angry at, zuko?

340
00:21:46,339 --> 00:21:49,041
Everyone... I don't know.

341
00:21:49,042 --> 00:21:49,942
Is it dad?

342
00:21:49,943 --> 00:21:51,477
No, no.

343
00:21:51,578 --> 00:21:52,845
Your uncle?
Me?

344
00:21:52,946 --> 00:21:54,880
No, no... no, no.

345
00:21:54,981 --> 00:21:56,048
Then who?

346
00:21:56,049 --> 00:21:57,182
Who are you angry at?

347
00:21:57,183 --> 00:21:58,650
Answer the question, zuko.

348
00:21:58,651 --> 00:21:59,785
Talk to us.

349
00:21:59,786 --> 00:22:01,186
Come on, answer the question.

