00:22:01,187 --> 00:22:02,688
Come on, answer it.

351
00:22:02,789 --> 00:22:05,591
I'm angry at myself.

352
00:22:10,196 --> 00:22:11,397
Why?

353
00:22:11,498 --> 00:22:13,932
Because I'm confused.

354
00:22:13,933 --> 00:22:15,968
Because I'm not sure
I know the difference

355
00:22:15,969 --> 00:22:17,736
between right
and wrong anymore.

356
00:22:17,737 --> 00:22:18,704
You're pathetic.

357
00:22:18,705 --> 00:22:22,074
I know one thing
I care about...

358
00:22:22,175 --> 00:22:24,109
I care about you.

359
00:22:27,814 --> 00:22:30,883
Well, those were wonderful
performances, everyone.

360
00:22:30,984 --> 00:22:33,952
I guess you wouldn't
understand, would you, azula

361
00:22:34,054 --> 00:22:35,921
because you're just so perfect.

362
00:22:36,022 --> 00:22:38,023
Well, yes, I guess you're right.

363
00:22:38,124 --> 00:22:40,325
I don't have sob stories
like all of you.

